+ * mod-attunement-plus
+ * Echoes of the Worldsoul stat application module for AzerothCore
+ *
+ * Applies absorbed stats from attuned items to players via the
+ * proper stat pipeline (ApplyStatBuffMod), so all secondary stats
+ * (attack power, spell power, health from stamina, etc.) update correctly.
+ *
+ * How it works:
+ *   1. On player login and stat update events, reads ap_item_snapshot
+ *      for this player's account, filtered by armor class.
+ *   2. Calculates absorbed stats using mastery rank, level scalar,
+ *      and talent bonuses stored in ap_mastery and ap_talents.
+ *   3. Applies the delta via ApplyStatBuffMod.
+ *   4. A WorldScript re-applies stats every 10 seconds to pick up
+ *      mid-session attunement changes without requiring a relog.
+ *
+ * License: GNU AGPL v3
+ */
